Are you concerned that you or your loved ones might die from the corona virus? You can help fix the problem. Corona virus is spreading and people are dying because doctors and nurses do not have the supplies needed to fight this pandemic.

The Governor of Illinois explained today that the corona virus is spreading and people are dying because doctors and nurses do not have the supplies needed to fight this pandemic. His state like other states needs "millions of masks, hundreds of thousands of gowns, gloves and medical equipment so Americans are being killed...I have people on the phones calling all over the world We are forced to compete and we are overpaying for the few medical supplies we are getting."

The Defense Production Act of 1950 is a United States federal law that authorizes the President to require businesses to fulfill orders deemed necessary for national defense and authorizes the President to requisition property, force industry to expand production and the supply of basic resources and prohibit price-gouging. Trump invoked the Defense Production Act in response to the corona virus but said he is not going to use it now. Business is profiting at the expense of American lives. We must stop pandemics like the corona virus that came from China and stop paying American companies from relocating in these countries.

American lives, jobs and the future of our great nation are at stake.
